32:02.355 --> 32:04.792
Now I'm...

32:04.835 --> 32:07.708
really gonna kill you.

32:11.146 --> 32:13.366
[panting]

32:19.285 --> 32:20.503
[sportscaster speaks
indistinctly on TV]

32:20.547 --> 32:23.289
Hey, get me a beer, will ya?

32:25.682 --> 32:28.120
[sportscaster continues
speaking indistinctly]

32:32.646 --> 32:33.995
Hello, Forest.

32:34.039 --> 32:36.867
Charlotte Richards,
what are you doing here?

32:36.911 --> 32:38.130
Oh, I just stopped by
to tell you

32:38.173 --> 32:39.522
that I know
about everything.

32:39.566 --> 32:42.482
Everyone,actually.

32:42.525 --> 32:45.398
Stephanie,
Diane, Jaylyn...

32:45.441 --> 32:47.530
about every woman
that you abused

32:47.574 --> 32:48.575
and then paid off.

32:48.618 --> 32:50.794
Most recently,
Mia, of course.

32:50.838 --> 32:52.535
She told me how
you actually got

32:52.579 --> 32:54.102
that cut on your head.

32:54.146 --> 32:55.799
I told her how you
were getting rough again.

32:55.843 --> 32:58.454
How you started
to strangle me.

32:58.498 --> 33:02.023
I tried to get you to
stop, but you wouldn't.

33:02.067 --> 33:03.764
So I pushed you.

33:03.807 --> 33:05.461
And you hit your head
against the lamp.

33:10.205 --> 33:11.598
How much do you want?

33:11.641 --> 33:12.686
CHARLOTTE:
Money?

33:12.729 --> 33:14.166
Well, a pattern

33:14.209 --> 33:16.733
of domestic abuse going
back decades is pretty bad.

33:16.777 --> 33:19.040
But murder?

33:19.084 --> 33:22.261
Whew, let's see,
carry the one...

33:22.304 --> 33:24.132
Yeah, all of it.

33:24.176 --> 33:26.569
Murder? What are you
talking about?

33:26.613 --> 33:29.268
Joanne Foles.
Ring a bell?

33:29.311 --> 33:31.879
You can stop
pretending, Forest.

33:31.922 --> 33:33.141
Cat's out of the bag.

33:33.185 --> 33:36.449
Or rather, the
bloody duffel bag.

33:36.492 --> 33:40.714
Yeah, you remember giving
that to Ben Sr., right?

33:40.757 --> 33:42.716
Well, see, hmm,

33:42.759 --> 33:44.805
he gave it to his young

33:44.848 --> 33:49.114
and hungry first-year
associate: me.

33:49.157 --> 33:52.160
And here's the
thing, I kept it.

33:52.204 --> 33:55.642
I thought it might
come in handy someday.

33:55.685 --> 33:59.037
I'll get my check book.

34:00.516 --> 34:03.171
Turns out
I'm a pretty smart lady.

34:05.913 --> 34:08.176
Not that smart.[gasps]

34:13.399 --> 34:15.618
Knock, knock.
It's Lucifer.

34:15.662 --> 34:17.490
Come to save the day.

34:17.533 --> 34:20.014
FOREST:
Everybody stay calm.

34:20.058 --> 34:21.189
Just get back
and I mean it.

34:21.233 --> 34:22.190
I mean it!

34:22.234 --> 34:23.496
Forest, let her go.

34:25.150 --> 34:27.978
Hey, I didn't mean
to kill Joanie.

34:28.022 --> 34:30.285
It was an accident.

34:30.329 --> 34:32.418
I'm sick. I need your help.

34:33.680 --> 34:35.116
Thanks for your help.

34:35.160 --> 34:38.554
I am not gonna help you
this time.

34:38.598 --> 34:39.903
[gun cocks]CHLOE: Hands up.

34:39.947 --> 34:41.209
Let her go, Forest.

34:43.472 --> 34:45.953
Was that enough of a confession,
Detective?

34:45.996 --> 34:47.085
Yes. We recorded everything.

34:47.128 --> 34:50.218
It's over, Forest.

34:50.262 --> 34:51.132
Let her go.

34:51.176 --> 34:53.482
[groans]

34:57.007 --> 34:58.357
Turn around.

34:58.400 --> 35:00.837
[handcuffs clicking]

35:11.065 --> 35:14.199
[laughs] Wow.

35:14.242 --> 35:16.288
It's a good place
to celebrate.

35:16.331 --> 35:18.812
Yes, it is.

35:18.855 --> 35:20.814
I have been coming here
ever since I realized

35:20.857 --> 35:23.295
that this may
be the closest

35:23.338 --> 35:25.601
to Heaven that
I'll ever get.

35:25.645 --> 35:28.865
Hmm.

35:28.909 --> 35:31.303
Me, too.

35:31.346 --> 35:33.479
You know, I've been
telling myself

35:33.522 --> 35:34.784
that I've been
doing God's work.

35:34.828 --> 35:37.874
But, uh, if I'm honest...

35:37.918 --> 35:40.486
I think I've been
doing it all for myself.

35:40.529 --> 35:43.880
To get my Father
to give me my wings back.

35:43.924 --> 35:46.883
[chuckles]

35:46.927 --> 35:50.148
But you know something,
Charlotte? I think, uh...

35:52.237 --> 35:55.892
I think I'm the one
who took my wings away.

35:55.936 --> 35:58.286
Great. We're both broken.

35:58.330 --> 35:59.766
[both laugh]

35:59.809 --> 36:01.289
Yeah.

36:01.333 --> 36:05.206
Well, I guess angels really are
just as flawed as humans,

36:05.250 --> 36:07.339
or at least I am.

36:07.382 --> 36:09.863
Hey, at least
we have each other.

36:09.906 --> 36:12.518
Tiny victories, right?

36:12.561 --> 36:13.823
Tiny?

36:13.867 --> 36:16.261
Uh, may I point out

36:16.304 --> 36:18.480
that you just stopped
a serial abuser?

36:18.524 --> 36:19.742
A murderer.

36:19.786 --> 36:21.875
Yeah, but that
doesn't change the fact

36:21.918 --> 36:25.966
that he hurt
a lot of women.

36:26.009 --> 36:28.142
No.

36:28.186 --> 36:31.711
But because of you...

36:31.754 --> 36:36.368
he will never hurt
anyone ever again.

36:36.411 --> 36:38.283
And I'm pretty sure
that you didn't do that

36:38.326 --> 36:42.417
