did you?

36:44.854 --> 36:47.248
[chuckles softly]
Maybe not.

36:49.337 --> 36:50.338
[chuckling]

36:50.382 --> 36:52.297
[rustling nearby]

36:53.385 --> 36:55.691
[gunshots]

36:55.735 --> 36:58.520
