37:22.544 --> 37:24.459
Well done, Detective.

37:29.421 --> 37:32.119
And, uh, point taken.

37:32.162 --> 37:34.426
What do you mean?

37:34.469 --> 37:36.732
Well, you put away not one,
but two bad guys today.

37:36.776 --> 37:38.125
All without my help.

37:38.168 --> 37:41.955
So it's become very
clear that you...

37:41.998 --> 37:43.739
well, you don't need me.

37:43.783 --> 37:45.088
That's okay, Detective,

37:45.132 --> 37:47.656
because with
that realization

37:47.700 --> 37:49.049
came another.

37:49.092 --> 37:51.094
Hmm.

37:51.138 --> 37:52.487
If you don't need me,

37:52.531 --> 37:54.968
then we've been
working together

37:55.011 --> 37:57.100
all this time
because you want to.

37:57.144 --> 38:01.409
Because you choose to.

38:01.453 --> 38:04.717
You did choose me.

38:04.760 --> 38:06.849
You were right.

38:06.893 --> 38:10.331
I've been trying to go back
to the way things were.

38:10.375 --> 38:12.115
You know, playing
our greatest hits,

38:12.159 --> 38:14.509
because I've been
avoiding dealing

38:14.553 --> 38:17.164
with things in
the present like...

38:17.207 --> 38:19.209
how I feel about you.

38:20.994 --> 38:22.952
I was afraid.

38:22.996 --> 38:25.694
Afraid...

38:25.738 --> 38:29.655
