38:39.142 --> 38:41.057
Lucifer.

38:41.101 --> 38:42.755
Detective, it's true.No.

38:42.798 --> 38:45.105
The other side of
me is... it's bad.

38:45.148 --> 38:48.674
It's monstrous, even.

38:48.717 --> 38:52.373
But you wanted the truth,
and you deserve the truth.

38:52.417 --> 38:54.114
Right now, I can't
show it to you,

38:54.157 --> 38:57.247
