have to tell you.

38:57.291 --> 38:59.772
Detective...

39:04.907 --> 39:08.868
Chloe...

39:08.911 --> 39:11.653
I am the Devil.

39:14.134 --> 39:16.005
No, you're not.

39:18.443 --> 39:20.575
Not to me.

39:31.456 --> 39:33.414
