39:33.458 --> 39:35.416
Oh. Oh.

39:35.460 --> 39:36.852
Let me turn this off.

39:36.896 --> 39:38.114
Right.

39:38.158 --> 39:39.768
Oh.

39:41.596 --> 39:43.381
Oh, it's...

39:43.424 --> 39:45.034
I'm so sorry.
I have to take this.

39:45.078 --> 39:46.906
Of course, no.

39:47.863 --> 39:51.084
Yeah.

39:51.127 --> 39:53.086
[inhales sharply]

39:53.129 --> 39:56.132
