39:56.176 --> 39:57.743
♪

39:57.786 --> 40:01.007
[gasps]

40:01.050 --> 40:03.444
Hey, just hold on, Charlotte.

40:03.488 --> 40:06.534
I'm, uh, I'm gonna get help.

40:06.578 --> 40:10.799
[gasps] I already
survived death once.

40:10.843 --> 40:14.716
I think twice is asking
too... [gasps] too much.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.718
